{
  "page": "Mya Rivers",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Mya Rivers</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Mya_Rivers_by_Riotarttherite.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Mya Rivers by Riotarttherite.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/38/Mya_Rivers_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/350px-Mya_Rivers_by_Riotarttherite.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"389\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/38/Mya_Rivers_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/525px-Mya_Rivers_by_Riotarttherite.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/38/Mya_Rivers_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/700px-Mya_Rivers_by_Riotarttherite.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Mya Rivers by Riotarttherite</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_172_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">172&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_173_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">173&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Melissa_Blackwood\" title=\"Melissa Blackwood\">Melissa Blackwood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Mya Rivers</b> was the eldest of the three bastard children of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a> and his sixth mistress, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Melissa_Blackwood\" title=\"Melissa Blackwood\">Melissa Blackwood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mya_Rivers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Melissa Blackwood \"reigned\" for five years as the mistress of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a>, during which she gave birth to three children: Mya, <a href=\"/index.php/Gwenys_Rivers\" title=\"Gwenys Rivers\">Gwenys</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden</a>. Aegon's bastards born of noblewomen were legitimized as <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Bastards\" title=\"Great Bastards\">Great Bastards</a> on the king's deathbed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mya_Rivers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\